Joan Cheever is the founder of The Chow Train non-profit food truck . 
  San Antonio police officers issued Cheever a $2,000 fine for feeding the homeless out of her personal pickup truck on April 7 . 
  Cheever founded the charity in 2005 and serves meals from her mobile kitchen . 
  She was cited for failure to serve food out of a licensed food truck because her personal vehicle is more compact . 
  The attorney and chef considers feeding the poor a free exercise of her faith . 
 